{"tid":1278048,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（戒丁）日清食品投資1.8億人幣珠海建新廠房","createTime":"2019-07-02T10:49:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T15:13:34.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7a64e87e650a4a9a1a9e8e6a7965a063296fd430","tid":1278048,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:49:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2019/07/02/2180293_b285461bfdafa919cea9b4022e7b626a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2019%2F07%2F02%2F2180293_b285461bfdafa919cea9b4022e7b626a.jpg&h=ff77fda2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日清食品(01475)宣布，計劃投資約1.8億元(人民幣‧下同)，在中國珠海興建新生產廠房生產包裝材料，以促進其在中國及香港的業務增長及發展。<br />\n<br />\n日清食品表示，旗下附屬公司與Grandview China Holdings Limited訂立股權轉讓協議，收購其於珠海聯智科技全部股權。珠海聯智科技擁有位於珠海的一幅佔地約3萬平方米的土地使用權。<br />\n<br />\n收購完成後，集團擬於該土地斥資約1.8億元，興建一座生產包裝材料的新廠房，計劃於2021年竣工。<br />\n<br />\n日清食品執行董事、董事長及首席執行官安藤清隆表示，新建的廠房將有助集團更有效控制生產成本，並能與現時營運中的生產設施產生協同效應。未來將繼續審視併購機會，藉此增強集團的優勢，以增加市場份額及取得可觀增長。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2180293\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2180293&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPm%2Fv5hJrJLSiIP9i8i%2FMgDc%3D&h=55693b85\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2180293</a>"},{"pid":"b8c3d4a31a16f3fd9b8064b3ab37472dfd928baa","tid":1278048,"uid":54126,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:54:22.000Z","msg":"奶共狗睇下幾時俾共產黨充公資產禁走資<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"521c1365198d355b45e5ea142b81a052ea875bbe","tid":1278048,"uid":41891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:30:10.000Z","msg":"在中國珠海興建新生產廠房生產包裝材料，以促進<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">其在中國及香港的業務增長及發展</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n支那一丁淨係俾支那人同香港人食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" c